http://www.thehindu.com/news/national/andhra-pradesh/Free-transport-facility-launched/article13990005.ece

East Godavari Collector H. Arun Kumar on Friday flagged off the free transport facility to NTR Beach Festival on the city outskirts.The 25 buses and 50 Tata Magic vehicles were provided by the Transport Department, which would travel from different parts of the city to the festival venue and in the return direction as well.Speaking on the occasion, Mr. Arun Kumar said that 25 buses and 50 Tata Magic vehicles would be operated between the beach and different residential colonies.Each bus would make four trips and each Magic vehicle would make eight trips a day during the festival, he said, adding that the service was free of cost and there was no need of paying any fare.